   398→bool check_flash_causal_non_square_seqlens(sdp_params const& params, bool debug) {
   399→  // FlashAttention 2 updated the default mask meaning for causal in this PR:
   400→  // 9e5e8bc91e it is now aligned to lower_right which would be a BC break
